data.description: Priced to sell! $16,000 less than original list price! No steps, no shoveling, no lawn mowing! Don't miss your chance to have everything you need on one floor! Built in 2000, this home offers a large living room, vaulted kitchen, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 baths and a laundry area.   Illuminated by two charming skylights, the kitchen has stainless steel appliances and a spacious dining area. Recent upgrades include new luxury vinyl plank flooring and the main bathroom has been updated with a 5' walk in shower with glass doors.  Step outside to discover a serene patio retreat enveloped by verdant landscaping, creating your private oasis at the rear of the property.   Positioned at the heart of the community, this centrally located residence is only steps away from downtown, the library and Grinnell College.  This remarkable home is an opportunity not to be missed! Schedule your viewing today to experience the unparalleled comfort and convenience it offers.
